#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:1
msgid "Form Editor"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:3
msgid ""
"The Form Editor lets you design Camunda Forms visually and export them as "
"`.form` files. Forms you create here are automatically available to the BPMN "
"Modeler for linking to `UserTask` and `StartEvent` elements."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:7
msgid "Opening the Form Editor"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:9
msgid ""
"Click the **Form Editor** icon (layout template / grid icon) in the left "
"sidebar. The editor opens with the form list on the left and the canvas area "
"on the right."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:11
msgid ""
"On your first visit, three example forms are pre-loaded automatically. Open "
"the **Kapvergunning Start** example to see a complete citizen-facing form "
"before creating your own."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:15
msgid "Exploring the example forms"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:17
msgid ""
"Select any entry in the form list to open it in the canvas. The three seed "
"examples are read-only (marked **EXAMPLE**) — you can inspect and export "
"them but not rename or delete them."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:26
msgid "Creating a new form"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:28
msgid "Click the blue **+** button at the top of the form list."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:29
msgid ""
"A new form called \"New Form\" appears in the list and the canvas opens with "
"an empty schema."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:30
msgid "Double-click the form name in the list to rename it."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:34
msgid "Building a form"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:36
msgid "The canvas is a full `@bpmn-io/form-js` graphical editor."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:43
msgid "Adding fields"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:45
msgid "Drag a component type from the left palette onto the canvas:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:47
msgid ""
"**Text field** — single-line text input, maps to a string process variable"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:48
msgid "**Number** — numeric input"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:49
msgid ""
"**Select** / **Radio** — option lists defined inline as `label / value` pairs"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:50
msgid "**Checkbox** — boolean field"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:51
msgid "**Text** — static display text, supports Markdown headings and lists"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:52
msgid ""
"**Button** — required at the end of every form with `action: submit` to "
"trigger the submit event"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:54
msgid ""
"!!! warning \"Submit button required\" `@bpmn-io/form-js` does not inject a "
"submit button automatically. Every form **must** end with a `Button` "
"component set to `action: submit`. Without it, the form renders but never "
"fires the submit event in Operaton."
msgstr ""

