#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:71
msgid "Saving a form"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:73
msgid ""
"Click **Save** in the toolbar. The button activates only when there are "
"unsaved changes. The schema is persisted to `localStorage` and immediately "
"available in the BPMN Modeler."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:77
msgid "Exporting a form as `.form`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:79
msgid ""
"Click **Export `.form`** to download the schema as a JSON file. The filename "
"is the form's schema ID (e.g., `kapvergunning-start.form`)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:81
