msgid "Operaton (direct REST deployment)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:85
msgid ""
"The BPMN Modeler's one-click deploy, which bundles `.form` files with the "
"BPMN automatically"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:89
msgid "Linking a form to a BPMN task"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:91
msgid ""
"You do not need to export the form to link it to a BPMN task. Forms saved in "
"the Form Editor appear automatically in the **Link to Form** dropdown in the "
"BPMN Modeler."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:93
msgid "Switch to the **BPMN Modeler** view."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:94
msgid "Select a `UserTask` or `StartEvent` on the canvas."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:95
msgid ""
"In the properties panel, find **Link to Form** and pick the form from the "
"dropdown."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:97
msgid ""
"See [BPMN Modeler — Linking a UserTask or StartEvent to a form]{1} for full "
"instructions."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:101
msgid "Renaming a form"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:103
msgid ""
"Double-click a form name in the list (WIP forms only) to activate inline "
"editing. Press **Enter** or click away to save the new name."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:107
msgid "Deleting a form"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:109
msgid ""
"Click the trash icon on a WIP form entry. A confirmation dialog appears "
"before the form is removed from `localStorage`. Example forms cannot be "
"deleted."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cform-editor.md:111
msgid ""
"!!! note If a deleted form is still referenced by a `camunda:formRef` in a "
"saved BPMN process, that reference becomes unresolvable. The BPMN Modeler "
"will still show the form ID in the properties panel, but the deploy modal "
"will list it as an unmatched form reference."
msgstr ""
